<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>emsenn.net</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/tech/domains/flatfile-agential-resource-system-date/</link><description>Recent content on emsenn.net</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://emsenn.net/library/tech/domains/flatfile-agential-resource-system-date/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title/><link>https://emsenn.net/library/tech/domains/flatfile-agential-resource-system-date/flatfile-agential-resource-system-date/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/tech/domains/flatfile-agential-resource-system-date/flatfile-agential-resource-system-date/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="flatfile-agential-resource-system-date"&gt;Flatfile Agential Resource System Date&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-is"&gt;What this is&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every entity in the &lt;a href="flatfile-agential-resource-system.md" class="link-internal"&gt;FlatfileAgentialResourceSystem&lt;/a&gt; carries its own temporal record in frontmatter.
An entity is not just what it says — it is also when it said it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="required-on-every-entity-file"&gt;Required on every entity file&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every entity file MUST carry:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;date-created&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;2026-03-18&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;date-modified&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;2026-03-18&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;date-created&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;a href="date-created.md" class="link-internal"&gt;date-created&lt;/a&gt;) — set once at creation, never changed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;date-modified&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;a href="date-modified.md" class="link-internal"&gt;date-modified&lt;/a&gt;) — updated each time the entity changes substantively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Both are &lt;a href="date.md" class="link-internal"&gt;Date&lt;/a&gt; values: &lt;code&gt;YYYY-MM-DD&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>